+ Usage

This is the BLOOD RAVEN THEME, a theme created by [[*user Dc_Yerko]] with indications of [[*user Kilerpoyo]] to be used in articles featuring the [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/valravn-corporation-hub Valravn Corporation].

To import this theme, just put this line in the upper part of your article:

> @@[[include theme:bloodraven]]@@

The blood of our open veins will cover the corpses of our enemies.

+ Usage of Color Variations

This theme has color variations, that is, alternative versions of the same theme but with some, or all, of its colors changed. This theme has 4 different color variations.

[[include component:image-block name=https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme:bloodraven/Screenshot_1.png|caption=FROSTBLOOD RAVEN|width=225px]]

++ FrostBlood Raven

This variation brings the bluest colors of winter and the fury of frostbyte to your screen.

Good for tales on winterlands.

To import the FrostBlood Raven variation, put the following at the upper part of your article:

> @@[[include theme:bloodraven |frostblood-raven= --]]]@@

[[include component:image-block name=https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme:bloodraven/Screenshot_2.png|caption=SUNBLOOD RAVEN|width=225px]]

++ SunBlood Raven

This variation brings the yellow and orange colors of the sun bouncing off the snow and burning the eyes of our enemies.

Good for when we need to talk about money.

To import the SunBlood Raven variation, put the following at the upper part of your article:

> @@[[include theme:bloodraven |sunblood-raven= --]]]@@

[[include component:image-block name=https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme:bloodraven/Screenshot_3.png|caption=ACIDBLOOD RAVEN|width=225px]]

++ AcidBlood Raven

This variation brings the green colors of the acidic blood that burns and corrodes the bodies of our enemies.

Good for when we are hacking and developing software.

To import the AcidBlood Raven variation, put the following at the upper part of your article:

> @@[[include theme:bloodraven |acidblood-raven= --]]]@@

[[include component:image-block name=https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme:bloodraven/Screenshot_4.png|caption=PALEBLOOD RAVEN|width=225px]]

++ PaleBlood Raven

This variation brings the pale colors of the blood-stained snow grave of our enemies.

Good for ethereal tales and cold endings.

To import the PaleBlood Raven variation, put the following at the upper part of your article:

> @@[[include theme:bloodraven |paleblood-raven= --]]]@@

